title: EYL #110 The Re-Up feat. Wallstreet Trapper

description:
In episode 110, we sat down with Wallstreet Trapper for another historic conversation. We spoke about not only making yourself a millionaire through investing, but guaranteeing that your children become millionaires. We discussed how to evaluate ETFs, how to find companies to invest in, growth stocks, investing in gold, how to use your health insurance to invest in stocks, the best ways to invest for your children and more.
